captions.text:
I'M HOME--
WHAT IN THE WORLD?

HONEY?
HONEY?

WHITNEY, THERE IS A GIANT SPIDER 
UNDER THE BOWL.

RUN FOR YOUR LIFE.
WE'LL RENDEZVOUS IN NOVA SCOTIA.

FOR CRYING OUT LOUD.
WHITNEY, OKAY I'VE PACKED OUR BAGS.

I BOUGHT OUR PLANE TICKET-- WHERE IS THE SPIDER?
IT WASN'T UNDER THE BOWL.

IT'S FREE?
CALL 9-1-1.

[TEXT NOTIFICATION] OH WAIT,
I'M GETTING A TEXT.

FROM YOU!
WHAT NO!

MY PHONE GOT TRAPPED 
UNDER THE BOWL WITH THE SPIDER.

ARE YOU REALLY SUGGESTING THAT A SPIDER IS
TEXT--

[TEXT NOTIFICATION] TIME TO DIE HUMANS...
WHAT?

WHAT'S GOING ON?
OKAY, WHEN I SAW IT THE FIRST THING I DID

WAS,
WELL REGRET NOT BUYING A FIREARM--

YEAH-- BUT THEN I TOOK MY
SHOE TO IT AND MISSED!

IT LAUNCHED IT AT ME SO I TRIED TO DODGE,
BUT THEN JUST RAN INTO THE WALL.

IT WAS ALL A BLUR, BUT BY SOME MIRACLE
TRAPPED IT UNDER THE BOWL.

THAT THING IS A NINJA.
[INDISTINCTIVE NOISE] DID YOU HEAR THAT?

YEAH.
LET'S JUST LEAVE.

OR BURN DOWN THE HOUSE.
OH IT'S LOCKED OR JAMMED OR SOMETHING!

[TEXT NOTIFICATION] YOU'RE NOT GETTING
OUT THAT EASILY.

NO.
[TEXT NOTIFICATION] I WOULDN'T TRY

THE KITCHEN EITHER.
[TEXT NOTIFICATION] AND THE WINDOWS ARE

COVERED IN SAUR KRAUT.
WHAT?

[TEXT NOTIFICATION] WEBS.
STUPID AUTO CORRECT.

HE TEXTS SO FAST.
WELL HE DOES HAVE EIGHT LEGS.

OH AND NOTHING IN THIS WORLD SHOULD HAVE EIGHT
LEGS.

YEAH, I KNOW.
OH, EXCEPT MAYBE AN OCTOPUS.

YEAH.
OR CONJOINED TWINS.

YEAH.
OR A CENTIPEDE THAT'S-- A CENTIPEDE THAT'S

HAD A REALLY HARD LIFE.
[TEXT NOTIFICATION] STOP TALKING.

[TEXT NOTIFICATION] AND START SCREAMING.
WHAT?
[SCREAMING]

JEREMY.
BRO, WHERE'S THE CAKE?

CAKE?
ADAM TEXTED ME TO COME OVER FOR CAKE. WHAT?
[SCREAMING]
THE LIGHTS AREN'T WORKING!

WAIT I'M GOING TO GO FIND THE CIRCUIT BREAKER.
JER- JEREMY DON'T LEAVE ME.

JEREMY?
JEREMY?

JEREMY?
JEREMY!

YOU'LL NEVER GET HIM BACK!
WHAT?

NO!
JEREMY!

JAMES?
HELP ME!

[SCREAMING] TAKE HER FIRST.
WHAT?

WHAT DO YOU MEAN?
OH.

I FOUND THE CAKE.
AND I KILLED A SPIDER.

[TEXT NOTIFICATION] GOODBYE CRUEL WORLD.
[SIGHS OF RELIEF] OH THANK YOU SO MUCH JEREMY.

[TEXT NOTIFICATION] P.S. I BEAT YOUR HIGH
SCORE ON BEJEWELED.

WHAT?
NO!
